snippet.title: Isly - Trailer
snippet.description:
Isly is an open-world, adventure, exploration and grindy video game inspired mainly by Stardew Valley and Forager.

You spawn on a small island with minimal resources.
You can generated other islands to find more resources and craft what you need!

PLAY THE GAME: https://yohanjabin.itch.io/isly
JOIN THE DISCORD: https://discord.gg/nzRVddcJgZ

Music: https://www.bensound.com/
